acfp       b*** ySend Chat Message b***ad   fb

fgSends a Chat message to one of the chat channels.

This is much like sending an x, but a chat message will be received by all
users who have that chat channel enabled.

Note that if you are harassed in chat messages, just like in express messages, 
you can quote a channel to the administration by pressing w<r"w>g.

Related commands:
w<rdw>g  - Configures your chat channels. 
w<r,w>g  - Chat wholist: Shows who is reading which channels.
